title: Amateur Photographer. 13 November 2010.
description:
Amateur Photographer. 13 November 2010.

Amateur Photographer is the world's oldest weekly magazine for 
photography enthusiasts. With its unique weekly format, it is 
the first for news and digital and film equipment tests. Regular 
features on reader portfolios, darkroom, digital, black & white 
and photographer profiles ensure all areas of photography are 
covered.

Enjoy.
